title: pixelmaker online
description:
Pixelmaker online is an action game that is minecraft quality clone with multiplayer  that gives you retro filing combined with modern quality. It takes the best from games like Minecraft, Quake ,COD and Counter-Strike and gives you fast action gameplay with tons of blood and flesh. Cubic soldiers fight against each other on alot of battle arenas using a deadly military arsenal. This is what multiplayer was invented for.
Game has 3 modes for now, deathmatch ,team deathmatch and zombie infection
